<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.4">
<l>māvali taṉṉuṭaiya makaṉvāṇaṉma kaḷirunta</l>
<l>kāvalaik kaṭṭaḻitta taṉikkāḷaika rutummalai</l>
<l>kōvalar kōvintaṉaik kuṟamātarkaḷ paṇkuṟiñcip</l>
<l>pāvoli pāṭinaṭam payilmāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that is desired by the solitary young man</l>
<l rend="indent">who destroyed the prison where sat the son of Mahābali</l>
<l rend="indent">and the daughter of Bāṇa,</l>
<l>that is Māliruñcōlai where women of the hill country perform,</l>
<l rend="indent">singing the sounds of melodious kuṟiñci verses</l>
<l>and dancing [in praise] of Govinda of the herders.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
